Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:14.78,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感情の名前なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:18.79,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言い出せばキリがないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:22.40,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君の目が叫ぶのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:26.46,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本能で聞き分ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.46,0:22:27.05,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trust
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:28.31,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}付き纏う
